@@ -20,9 +20,6 @@ This project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](http://semver.org/).
 ### Fixed
 
  - #3015, Fix unnecessary count() on RPC returning single - @steve-chavez
- - #1070, Fix HTTP status responses for upserts - @taimoorzaeem
